<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #e39cc2; 
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            left: 0; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: flex-end; 
            gap: 10px; 
            z-index: 1000; 
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .heading {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #e39cc2;
            margin-top: 60px; 
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .about {
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            gap: 20px; 
        }
        .about-image img {
            max-width: 100%; 
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px; 
        }
        .about-content {
            flex: 1; 
        }
        .about-content p {
            margin: 0; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
        
    </nav>

    <div class="heading">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Create joy and sell more</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="about">
            <div class="about-content">
                <p>We are a passionate team committed to providing our 
                customers with the finest products, handpicked and carefully 
                curated to meet your everyday needs. Whether you're looking 
                for the freshest produce, high-quality merchandise, or unique 
                artisanal items, we strive to offer a shopping experience that 
                is both enjoyable and trustworthy. We believe in building long-
                lasting relationships with our customers, offering exceptional 
                service and products that enhance your life. </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
